

### Get a list of people

GET http://localhost:1337/people HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json

### Adding a Person

POST http://localhost:1337/people HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "John",
    "lastName": "Savage"
}

### Getting a single person
GET http://localhost:1337/people/2 HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json